        <h3><u>Transportation</u></h3>
        <p> <strong>The California transportation system</strong> helps to move people and goods around and through the state. The aim of this primer is to provide policymakers and the public with key information about this system.</p>
        <p>For more information click on <a style="color: yellow;" href="https://lao.ca.gov/"><strong>California's Transportation System</strong></a></p>
      </div>
